"{\"uid\": \"nbclosangeles.com-entertainment-entertainment-news-tom-cruises-surprising-paycheck-2024-olympics-stunt-paris-3510977\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The star-studded Closing Ceremony featured lots of music and stunts from a Hollywood icon.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 84, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999994613518, \"rank\": 5.385629245626157e-10, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Originally appeared onE!\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Online  It wasn't mission impossible forTom Cruiseto deliver the Olympic flag to Los Angeles after the2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 5.15309158895545e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 224, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream Los Angeles News for free, 24/7, wherever you are.\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 5.15309158895545e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But as it turns out, the \\\"Top Gun\\\" star agreed to pull offhis dazzling death-defying stuntwithout receiving a paycheck.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We pitched on a Zoom,\\\" 2028 L.A. Olympics president and chairperson Casey Wasserman said of the Closing Ceremony during a CNBC panel on Sept. 11.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 490, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Casey Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\"}, {\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999964124981, \"rank\": 3.2418298334019164e-09, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"About five minutes in the presentation, he goes, 'I am in.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am only doing it if I can do everything.'\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every step of the way, he got more involved and more engaged-and by the way, he did it all for free.\\\"\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"E!\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News has reached out to reps for Cruise for comment but has not heard back.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a surprise for Wasserman and executive producer Ben Winston, who initially wanted to make the performance as easy as possible for Cruise to take part.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"score\": 0.9998465312535559, \"rank\": 0.00015344849054279216, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\"}, {\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Winston\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ben Winston\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Winston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Winston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The original idea was a person in the stadium as a stunt double,\\\" Wasserman recalled.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1085, \"end\": 1094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"score\": 0.9998465312535559, \"rank\": 0.00015344849054279216, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are like, 'Well, there is no way we are getting this.\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to get four hours of filming time.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will do the thing in L.A. with the Hollywood sign, he will hand the thing off and he's done.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999970652563523, \"rank\": 2.934537000597258e-06, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe we will get the other stuff and the rest will be just a stunt double.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Cruise wanted to really be a part of the performance.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Winston could not help but gush over his commitment to the project.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think there is anybody like him in the world,\\\" he toldThe Hollywood Reporterlast month.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no better collaborator.\\\"\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, when the producer informed the\\\"Mission: Impossible\\\"actor that a stunt double would do the heavy lifting, he replied, \\\"We are not doing a stuntman in a balaclava.\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to be the one who jumps off the roof, and I am going to be the one who drives through Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999970757472, \"rank\": 2.9242546408327618e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for why they wanted Cruise for the honor?\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1974, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not really think who else would work,\\\" Winston admitted to the outlet.\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Who else is synonymous with action and an American hero?\\\"\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2097, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9957020503745059, \"rank\": 0.00428346588218832, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 62-year-old's stunt that closed the chapter on this year's Olympic Games will surely go down in history.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Cruise dove into the stadium, Los Angeles Mayor Karen Bass andSimone Bilespresented him with the Olympic flag before he took it back to Los Angeles in true \\\"Mission: Impossible\\\" fashion.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2259, \"end\": 2270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 5.15309158895545e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 2365, \"end\": 2376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 5.15309158895545e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because for Cruise, moving the goalpost for each project is crucial.\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am always pushing,\\\" he toldBusiness Insiderlast June.\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just remember, every time they say, 'Can you top it?\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can you not top it?'\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are always pushing.\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every film I do, whatever genre it's in, I want to make it as entertaining as possible for that audience.\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I can do things better.\\\"\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": []}]}"